om%2Fterms&d=REZNLD6XKc%2F2J9Njm9EJufno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=4b92786d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mewe.com/terms</a><br />\n<blockquote>幾時會俾同點俾法都無講。最後，如果有日想修改刪除自己係佢哋公司嘅個人資料時又無講可以點做。更無講啲資料會儲幾耐，自己又唔可以下載返<br />\n</blockquote>MeWe 嘅 Terms 清楚過Mastodon , 答晒你話人冇講啲野啦.<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>而要課金sub 先有End to End encryption，今時今日真係唔可以話係合格嘅做法</blockquote><br />\n唔合格? 仲唔明 nothing is for free?"}],"pinned":{"pid":"3fb216059f3493657d244fd63963cf8f7ad2369e","tid":2363834,"uid":276887,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T13:42:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5hewBan.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5hewBan.jpg&h=5de53ba9&s={SIZE}\" />"}}